-relationships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003etrack relationships with your supporters\u003c/a\u003e.¬†","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"\u003ci\u003eüìå Note: A supporter cannot be added to a path for pledging on a moneybomb page.\u003c/i\u003e","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/126851769/7478f86a45ec333090032305/Screen_Shot_2019-06-10_at_10_04_07_AM.png","width":1962,"height":2262,"align":"center"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Under \u003cb\u003e[Page Type] Settings\u003c/b\u003e, check ‚ÄúAdd to path‚Äù and add the appropriate information for path (e.g. \"Become a donor\"), path assigned to (overall point person), step (a specific step on a path), step point person (if different from the overall path point person), and step due date (optional). Click \u003cb\u003eSave settings\u003c/b\u003e.","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Once someone takes the action and is added to a path, the path will display on their profile and you can view how far along on that path they are.\u0026nbsp;","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/111487079/6c4cb84f16194fae86481faf/Screen_Shot_2019-03-27_at_9_32_18_AM.png","width":1078,"height":479,"align":"center"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"You can \u003ca href=\"https://support.nationbuilder.com/people/target-people/how-to-target-people\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003efilter\u003c/a\u003e to find people on specific paths, completed paths, abandoned paths, etc.¬†","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"heading","text":"Step 6: Where does a person go next?","idAttribute":"step-6-where-does-a-person-go-next"},{"t